        "text": "Psalm 8:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " with the use of other verbs. ידע in the sense of loving intimacy; חשּׁב, properly to count, compute, here rationem habere. Instead of כּי followed by the future there are consecutive futures here, and בּן־אדם is aramaizingly (בּר אנשׁ) metamorphosed into בּן־אנושׁ. ",
        "children": []
